One the one hand, most 00 languages do have some distributed extension, and almost every new architectural development in the distributed system community is, to some extent, object-based. On the other hand, 00 technology is particularly emerging in the field of distributed dependable systems, and 00 flexibility and reusability features are very appealing to handle the complexity of these systemsThis morkshop aimed at bringing together researchers and developers from academia and industry, who are advancing the stateof-the-art in dependable distributed 00 systems, or are experimenting with dependable distributed 00 systems in industrial applications. The workshop topics included: